{"actor":"claude-code","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-02-17T21:25:23Z","event_type":"status_changed","id":49,"issue_id":"beefcake-swarm-jtj","new_value":"{\"status\":\"in_progress\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"beefcake-swarm-jtj\",\"title\":\"Add blast-radius guard to write_file (reject \\u003e50% shrink of existing files)\",\"description\":\"Even with edit_file available, workers may still use write_file on existing files. At 5-15 tok/s, local models lose context and truncate, destroying files. Add a guard in WriteFileTool::call() that reads the existing file size, and if the new content is \\u003c50% of the original, returns an error telling the worker to use edit_file instead. Files: crates/swarm-agents/src/tools/fs_tools.rs\",\"notes\":\"EVIDENCE from job 1653: worker replaced 500-line pipeline.rs with 'tool_response content not available'. Blast-radius guard would have caught \\u003e99% shrink.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":0,\"issue_type\":\"bug\",\"owner\":\"squires.b@gmail.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-17T09:09:48Z\",\"created_by\":\"TheFermiSea\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-18T03:17:37Z\"}"}
